ai-ja294:1.1_0: “What is Bāhiya of the Bark Robe,
ai-ja294:1.3_0: trunk, Ambaṭṭha, with branches and leaves,
ai-ja294:2.1_0: I was born in a family of child,
ai-ja294:2.2_0: you’re praised by the good family.
ai-ja294:2.3_0: The heap of gold coins and bullion
ai-ja294:3.2_0: who lies down together when they lie.
ai-ja294:3.4_0: even if they praise each other.”
